Summary by Ground News Lafayette Commodores (8-5) defeated Water Valley 24-10 on Wednesday night. Lafayette scored 12 runs in the first two innings with nine coming in the second. Luke Anderson went 2-for-4 and scored three runs with five RBIs. Share menu 1 Articles 1 Articles All Left Center Right
